### 异常路径：project_id 小于等于 0，预期 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{invalidProjectId}}/nodes/{{repeatableAdminCompleteNodeId}}/complete
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：node_id 小于等于 0，预期 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminCompleteNodeProjectId}}/nodes/{{invalidNodeId}}/complete
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：请求体不是 JSON 对象，预期 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminCompleteNodeProjectId}}/nodes/{{repeatableAdminCompleteNodeId}}/complete
Content-Type: application/json

[]

### 异常路径：项目不存在，预期 404
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{missingProjectId}}/nodes/{{repeatableAdminCompleteNodeId}}/complete
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：阶段节点不存在，预期 404
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminCompleteNodeProjectId}}/nodes/{{missingNodeId}}/complete
Content-Type: application/json

{}
